		<b>Comment By Steve, 11-10-10</b>
		<p>Fishing in Montana?  Didn't know Yosemite Park was in Montana.</p>
		
		<b>Comment By Jenny Shank, 11-10-10</b>
		<p>Steve,<br />
<br />
You're right.  The Grossenbachers are based in Bozeman and they are experts on Montana fly fishing, but the Oprah show flew them out to California for the fishing expedition.  According to the About.Com Q&A;, Oprah did tell Brian Grossenbacher that she plans to visit Montana to fish with them again.  Sorry for the error, and thanks for pointing it out!  I've corrected it above.</p>
		
